  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示团队在使用群件工具时的典型协作路径。起点是团队聊天室，成员在那里讨论需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，聊天室作为入口。接下来是直接进入看板，还是需要先经过某个决策点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "聊天室直接连到看板，但看板本身是一个决策节点——菱形。从看板出发有两条路径：一条是链式推进到迭代待办列表，另一条是通过认证回到聊天室确认某些事项。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把看板设为菱形决策节点，标注\"chain\"到迭代待办，\"attestation\"回到聊天室。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "迭代待办和经过认证的聊天室，这两条线最终都要汇聚到问题追踪器。问题追踪器也是一个决策点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：迭代待办直接连到问题追踪器，聊天室经过认证后也连到同一个问题追踪器，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，两条线都汇入问题追踪器。然后问题追踪器要做一个判断：如果问题确认成立，走\"yes\"分支回到看板更新状态；如果不成立，走\"no\"分支退回聊天室重新讨论。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加问题追踪器作为菱形节点，标注\"yes\"到看板，\"no\"到聊天室。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "从看板确认问题后，还需要经过知识库页面做最后的部署决策。这个页面要判断是自托管还是SaaS模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "知识库页面也是菱形决策节点吗？两种部署方式分别指向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，菱形。自托管模式回到看板进行本地部署配置；SaaS模式则回到聊天室通知团队使用云端服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。知识库页面标注\"self-hosted\"到看板，\"SaaS\"到聊天室。整个流程闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_WikiPage",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我再看一下，问题追踪器到看板的那条\"yes\"分支，是不是应该更明确一点？比如确认问题的状态更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前标注是\"yes\"，需要改成\"confirmed\"或者\"verified\"吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不用改，保持\"yes\"和\"no\"更简洁。但我发现一个问题：看板到迭代待办的连接，我之前说的是直接连，但应该是带标签的。请加上\"chain\"标签。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，看板到迭代待办明确标注为\"chain\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再看认证那条线，看板通过\"attestation\"回到聊天室，这个逻辑是团队成员在看板上标记需要确认的事项，然后回到聊天室@相关人员。没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解正确。整个流程我梳理一下：聊天室→看板（决策）→迭代待办/认证回聊天室→问题追踪器（决策）→看板/聊天室→知识库（决策）→看板/聊天室。所有菱形节点都处理完毕。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现迭代待办和问题追踪器之间的连接，你画的是直接连线，但按照我们的工具链，应该是任务卡片自动同步的。这个需要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前是无标签的直接连接。如果需要体现同步机制，我可以加个标签比如\"sync\"或\"auto-create\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不用加标签了，保持简洁。但请确认迭代待办和问题追踪器、以及认证后的聊天室和问题追踪器，这两条汇入线都是无标签的直连，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。迭代待办直连问题追踪器，认证后的聊天室也直连问题追踪器，均无标签。所有带标签的连接只有：chain、attestation、yes、no、self-hosted、SaaS。流程图已完成。",
